            "heading": "What are Cherokee FORM women's scrubs?",
            "content": "Cherokee FORM women's scrubs are premium knit scrubs designed for healthcare professionals who want elevated style without sacrificing performance. Combining the polished look of woven fabric with the comfort, stretch, and durability of knitwear, FORM delivers a modern, sophisticated feel that moves with you throughout every shift. The collection is designed to offer a refined fit, versatile styling, and all-day comfort for today's healthcare workplace."
