        "item_QpK6fE": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What fabric and technology is used in Cherokee FORM women's scrubs?",
            "content": "FORM scrubs are made with a premium 86% nylon and 14% spandex blend, featuring Cherokee's exclusive 360º Stretch technology. The fabric combines the appearance of woven fabric with the resilience of knitwear — it follows your shape for a polished look and feel through even the longest shifts. Power-mesh panels are incorporated into select styles for added fashionable flexibility. The fabric is moisture-wicking and easy-care, and the super-smooth surface gives FORM its distinctive elevated finish."
          }
