        "item_YBKaEA": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do Cherokee FORM women's scrubs fit?",
            "content": "FORM scrubs are designed with a flattering drape and stylish lines that follow your shape — not baggy, not restrictive. The 360º Stretch fabric moves with you in every direction while maintaining a polished, structured look. Pant silhouettes range from a trouser cut for a tailored, professional look to a mid rise tapered leg and a mid rise jogger for a more fitted, contemporary fit. Tops include standard V-neck lengths and tuck-in styles for a clean tucked look. FORM is built for healthcare professionals who want their <a href=\"https://www.cherokeeuniforms.com/cherokee-womens-scrubs\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">scrubs</span></a> to look as put-together as they do."
          }
        },
