          "settings": {
            "heading": "What makes Cherokee FORM different from other Cherokee scrubs?",
            "content": "FORM is Cherokee's most elevated line — designed specifically for healthcare professionals who appreciate sophisticated workwear. The key differences are the fabric system and the finish. The premium 86% nylon and 14% spandex blend with 360º Stretch technology gives FORM the appearance of woven fabric — structured and polished — with the stretch and comfort of knitwear underneath. Power-mesh panels add breathability without breaking the clean aesthetic. Signature details like antique copper hardware set FORM apart visually from the rest of the Cherokee scrubs. For professionals who want scrubs that look refined on the floor, FORM is that line."
